      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single ASTM F1717 load configuration (15° offset, 35 mm segment length). Although this is the standard regulatory configuration, it represents only one point in the COU space. Achieved level (2) is below the required level (3); this gap is documented as an accepted limitation by the decision team."
