    "rationale": "Overall credibility is sufficient for the intended regulatory use. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) reflects the standard regulatory test protocol constraint and is accepted given that the single F1717 configuration is the normative basis for FDA submission. All three QoIs pass both E/uval and percentage-difference acceptance criteria across two independent laboratories.",
